#: of numpy.random.RandomState.negative_binomial:33
msgid ""
"Drawn samples from the parameterized negative binomial distribution, where "
"each sample is equal to N, the number of failures that occurred before a "
"total of n successes was reached."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/random/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.random.RandomState.negative_binomial:38
msgid ""
"This function returns the C-long dtype, which is 32bit on windows and "
"otherwise 64bit on 64bit platforms (and 32bit on 32bit ones). Since NumPy "
"2.0, NumPy's default integer is 32bit on 32bit platforms and 64bit on 64bit "
"platforms."
msgstr ""

